{"tid":2284004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句說話比你睇到侵侵有幾勁幾有遠見幾敢言！！！！！！！","createTime":"2020-11-13T03:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:37:06.000Z","uid":199670,"like":29,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8590a78b597acd36b911b48200317824c43f89","tid":2284004,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】特朗普：世衛上調死亡率至 3.4% 不真確　「直覺遠低於 1%」<br />\n<br />\n世衛3月初上調武漢肺炎（COVID-19）的死亡率，由先前估計的約 2%，上調至3.4%，亦高於季節性流感少於 1% 的死亡率。 但美國總統特朗普3月4日表示， <span class=\"red\">3.4% 是假數值（false number），認為有不少病情較輕的病人都沒有申報，有很多病情較輕、很快康復的病人，根本沒有求診，患病的人相信比現在掌握的數據多，因此武漢肺炎的死亡率應只有少於 1%。</span><br />\n<br />\n當時，美國有超過 230 宗確診個案，12 人死亡，死亡率 5.4%，不單高於世衛的 3.4%，亦比中國的 3.7% 高。"},{"pid":"877a48eb8424eca270d8bdf1ea7b6a5c73da17e4","tid":2284004,"uid":199670,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:42:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%AE%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E7%8E%87%E8%87%B3-3-4-%E4%B8%8D%E7%9C%9F%E7%A2%BA-%E7%9B%B4%E8%A6%BA%E9%81%A0%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC-1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E7%258E%2587%25E8%2587%25B3-3-4-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%25A2%25BA-%25E7%259B%25B4%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E9%2581%25A0%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%2596%25BC-1%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOInWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=2983b1df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E4%25B8%2596%25E8%25A1%259B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E7%258E%2587%25E8%25